Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.12,0:00:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 信乃也好 庄介也好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.29,0:00:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这么晚了也不联系一下 干什么去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.20,0:00:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心的话让五狐去找找看怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.19,0:00:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 我又没在担心他们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.61,0:00:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 滨路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要不要去学校参观
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.07,0:00:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正小信和庄介也会暂时滞留一段时间的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 对你来说学校就是必要的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.28,0:00:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.87,0:00:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庄介
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.87,0:00:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 伤口并不是很深
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨 快去通知里见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.65,0:01:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.27,0:01:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再动了 庄介
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 没想到这个家伙会派上用场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.63,0:01:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.85,0:01:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把它放进你外套的口袋里了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别擅自放进来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.84,0:01:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.23,0:01:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 是那位鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.46,0:01:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.47,0:01:35.02,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.47,0:01:35.02,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.02,0:01:38.40,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.02,0:01:38.40,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.40,0:01:42.90,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.40,0:01:42.90,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.78,0:01:49.20,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乾いた風に抱かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.78,0:01:49.20,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}迎面吹着干燥的风
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.20,0:01:55.66,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生命への 真偽を覚え 刻む想い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.20,0:01:55.66,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}懂得了生命的真伪 铭刻于心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:01:59.08,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}ただ 傍に居たいと願い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:01:59.08,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是 祈愿待在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.21,0:02:01.88,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人を愛し 人を憎み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.21,0:02:01.88,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱过 恨过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:05.34,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲しさは  優しさ生む
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:05.34,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲伤最后化作温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.34,0:02:10.30,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}例え光が 消えたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.34,0:02:10.30,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算陷入无尽黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:15.14,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日の希望を探すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:15.14,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仍会寻觅明日希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:19.27,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃えた血の呼吸 消え寄せれば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:19.27,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃烧的血液 停止了呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:24.40,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果は奇跡に変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:24.40,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果之缘 最终转化成奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:26.45,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:26.45,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.49,0:02:29.03,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.49,0:02:29.03,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:32.03,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}闇を搔き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:32.03,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拨开黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:36.50,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}手を伸ばすよ どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:36.50,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}伸手向前 追寻你到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:38.87,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:38.87,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:42.34,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}いつか 変えるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:42.34,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总有一天 命运将会转变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.46,0:02:47.05,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}涙の意味 無駄にはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.46,0:02:47.05,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要让眼泪白流
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.05,0:02:51.72,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}螺旋のように 蠢く果てに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.05,0:02:51.72,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如螺旋一般交织骚动的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:54.26,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吠えて 交わる FATE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:54.22,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}狂吠吧 交织的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能让那鬼和孩子逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把他们找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 也不要忘了那把刀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是传说中的妖刀——村雨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在那种小鬼手上
